query:
UPDATE leases
            SET
                leased = ?4, expires_at = ?5, probation = ?6, client_id = ?7
            WHERE ip in
               (
                    SELECT ip
                    FROM leases
                    WHERE
                        ((expires_at > ?1) AND (client_id = ?2) AND (ip = ?3))
                    ORDER BY ip LIMIT 1
                )
            RETURNING ip
